  <brief_title>Impact of a Self-Administered Information Leaflet on Adequacy of Colonic Cleansing for in-Hospital Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Impact of a Self-Administered Information Leaflet on Adequacy of Colonic Cleansing for in-Hospital</official_title>
